4plus1-architecture-skills

This project contains independently written AI assistant rules and skills for
software architecture modeling.

It is inspired by public software architecture modeling practices and concepts
from Huawei Cloud CodeArts Modeling documentation. The original vendor PDF or
documentation is not redistributed in this repository.

